== Transfer Phase ==

... DFSP A initiates a normal Mojaloop P2P Transfer ...

D2 -> D2: Generate a new ""transferId"", and associate \n it with the ""transactionRequestId""

rnote over D2 #Light
**""POST /transfers""**
""FSPIOP-Source: dfspa""
""FSPIOP-Destination: dfspb""
{
  "transferId": "55555555-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "payerFsp": "dfspa",
  "payeeFsp": "dfspb",
  "amount": {
    "amount": "100",
    "currency": "USD"
  },
  "expiration": "2020-06-15T13:00:00.000",
  "ilpPacket": "...",
  "condition": "...",
}
end note
D2 -> S: ""POST /transfers""
S --> D2: ""202 Accepted""

rnote over S #Light
**""POST /transfers""**
""FSPIOP-Source: dfspa""
""FSPIOP-Destination: dfspb""
{
  "transferId": "55555555-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "payerFsp": "dfspa",
  "payeeFsp": "dfspb",
